<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Description">Description</span></h2>
<p><b>Mithril Lumps</b> can be obtained by mining <a href="/Games/Lord_of_the_Test/Mithril_Ore" title="Games/Lord of the Test/Mithril Ore">Mithril Ore</a>. 
</p><p>They can also be <a href="/Smelting" class="mw-redirect" title="Smelting">smelted</a> into <a href="/Games/Lord_of_the_Test/Mithril_Ingot" title="Games/Lord of the Test/Mithril Ingot">Mithril Ingots</a> with the help of a <a href="/Furnace" title="Furnace">Furnace</a>.
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Smelting">Smelting</span></h2>
<table class="wikitable">

<tbody><tr>
