</th>
<th>Description
</th></tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/Mithril_Lump" title="Mithril Lump"><img alt="Mithril Lump.png" src="/images/thumb/f/ff/Mithril_Lump.png/32px-Mithril_Lump.png" decoding="async" width="32" height="32" srcset="/images/thumb/f/ff/Mithril_Lump.png/48px-Mithril_Lump.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/ff/Mithril_Lump.png/64px-Mithril_Lump.png 2x" /></a> <b>Mithril Lump</b>
</td>
<td><img alt="Arrow.png" src="/images/4/41/Arrow.png" decoding="async" width="32" height="26" /> <img alt="Furnace.png" src="/images/thumb/0/0f/Furnace.png/24px-Furnace.png" decoding="async" width="24" height="24" srcset="/images/thumb/0/0f/Furnace.png/36px-Furnace.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0f/Furnace.png/48px-Furnace.png 2x" /> <img alt="Arrow.png" src="/images/4/41/Arrow.png" decoding="async" width="32" height="26" />
</td>
<td><a href="/Mithril_Ingot" title="Mithril Ingot"><img alt="Mithril Ingot.png" src="/images/thumb/4/45/Mithril_Ingot.png/32px-Mithril_Ingot.png" decoding="async" width="32" height="32" srcset="/images/thumb/4/45/Mithril_Ingot.png/48px-Mithril_Ingot.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Mithril_Ingot.png/64px-Mithril_Ingot.png 2x" /></a> <a href="/Games/Lord_of_the_Test/Mithril_Ingot" title="Games/Lord of the Test/Mithril Ingot">Mithril Ingot</a>
</td>
<td>Used for <a href="/Crafting" title="Crafting">crafting</a> <a href="/Games/Lord_of_the_Test/Armor" title="Games/Lord of the Test/Armor">Armor</a> or <a href="/Tool" title="Tool">Tools</a>.
